videos.description: Vasturia gets out on the fast break and finishes to get Notre Dame off and running against Duke.
videos.headline: Steve Vasturia gets Notre Dame off to fast start

videos.description: Grayson Allen makes the 3-point basket off a great rebound and pass by Luke Kennard.
videos.headline: Duke caps 10-2 run with Grayson Allen 3-pointer

videos.description: Luke Kennard makes reverse lay in
videos.headline: Kennard finishes play with nice reverse lay in

videos.description: Duke Interim Head Coach Jeff Capel talks about the first half defensive performance and the need to execute offensively in the second half
videos.headline: Duke Interim Head Coach Jeff Capel talks about the first half defensive performance and the need to execute offensively in the second half

videos.description: After an offensive foul call Notre Dame Head Coach Mike Brey is called for a technical foul.
videos.headline: Notre Dame Head Coach Mike Brey goes nuts after call

videos.description: V.J. Beachem streaks right through the lane, taking the inbounds pass and throwing down the monster two-handed dunk for Notre Dame.
videos.headline: V.J. Beachem throws down big dunk off inbound play

videos.description: Just when Notre Dame needed it, the Fighting Irish go on an 8-0 run to claw back to within striking distance of Duke.
videos.headline: Notre Dame 8-0 run gets the Irish back in the game

videos.description: After Notre Dame cuts the lead down to one, Grayson Allen drains a clutch 3-pointer to get Duke back on track.
videos.headline: Grayson Allen makes crucial 3-pointer

videos.description: Duke's Grayson Allen talks about his teams effort in their 84-74 win over Notre Dame
videos.headline: Duke's Grayson Allen talks about his teams effort in their 84-74 win over Notre Dame
